title: the.fugitive.406.dvdrip.xvid-ositv
description:
The Fugitive.S04E06.Joshua's Kingdom.DVDRip by OSiTV (with English subtitles)


For those who wish to play the show on stand-alone DVD players, I'm going to upload the episodes in avi format, including English subtitles.

The upload of the mkv files will continue also - the mkv files are slightly better in video quality with higher resolution, but they don't have subtitles and can't be played on stand-alone DVD players.
